{
    "publish_date": "2013-04-02T15:20:09.000Z", 
    "score": 0.00031853529163290885, 
    "video_length": "PT9M48S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "5.746", 
            "start": "7.354"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-A year ago, most of the West\nsaw Mali as a kind of cultural", 
            "dur": "3.139", 
            "start": "13.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "center of Africa, a place with\ncelebrated musicians and a", 
            "dur": "3.101", 
            "start": "16.239"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "healthy tourist trade.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "19.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that all changed when the\nbungled military coup in the", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "23.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "south led to a jihadist\ntake-over in the north.", 
            "dur": "3.08", 
            "start": "26.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Islamist groups like Ansar Dine\nand MUJAO imposed a harsh", 
            "dur": "3.83", 
            "start": "29.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "system of sharia law in northern\ncities like Gao and", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "33.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Timbuktu, banning everything\nfrom booze and cigarettes to", 
            "dur": "3.4", 
            "start": "36.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "music and dancing.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "39.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In January, the Islamists\nlaunched a second offensive,", 
            "dur": "3.29", 
            "start": "44.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sending the Malian army running\nand forcing France,", 
            "dur": "2.85", 
            "start": "47.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Mali&#39;s former colonial\nruler, to intervene.", 
            "dur": "2.446", 
            "start": "50.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In a matter of days, French\ntroops had recaptured all of", 
            "dur": "3.08", 
            "start": "56.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "northern Mali&#39;s major towns\nfrom the rebels.", 
            "dur": "3.69", 
            "start": "59.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It looked like the quickest,\ncleanest, most successful war", 
            "dur": "2.95", 
            "start": "62.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of modern times.", 
            "dur": "3.15", 
            "start": "65.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But things aren&#39;t ever\nthat simple.", 
            "dur": "2.18", 
            "start": "69.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now the Malians and the French\nare facing a vicious", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "71.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Afghanistan-style war against\npockets of invisible Muslim", 
            "dur": "3.6", 
            "start": "73.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "insurgents in a fight with\nno real end in sight.", 
            "dur": "3.51", 
            "start": "77.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the story of the battle\nfor Gao, the biggest", 
            "dur": "2.45", 
            "start": "99.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "city in northern Mali.", 
            "dur": "3.01", 
            "start": "101.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The surrounding countryside is\nstill jihadist territory.", 
            "dur": "2.82", 
            "start": "104.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And though the French control\nthe city center--", 
            "dur": "2.07", 
            "start": "107.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "more or less--", 
            "dur": "1.04", 
            "start": "109.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "everyday, new homemade bombs\nare found in the city, each", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "110.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one powerful enough\nto destroy a tank.", 
            "dur": "3.54", 
            "start": "114.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The French and their\nMalian allies", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "117.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "need to keep Gao secure.", 
            "dur": "1.34", 
            "start": "119.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And to do that, they need to\nexpel the surrounding rebels.", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "120.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Where do you think\nthe rebels are?", 
            "dur": "2.865", 
            "start": "126.075"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-At Gao&#39;s only hotel, the Malian\ntroops seemed relaxed,", 
            "dur": "3.885", 
            "start": "142.545"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even though there was clearly\ntrouble on the horizon.", 
            "dur": "2.608", 
            "start": "146.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[GUN FIRE]", 
            "dur": "13.672", 
            "start": "149.038"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.572", 
            "start": "162.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "164.282"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-I jumped in the back of a\nMalian pickup truck heading", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "170.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "towards the battle through\ndeserted streets.", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "172.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The French were leaving this\nbattle to the Malians.", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "175.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But no one knew what\nto expect.", 
            "dur": "1.53", 
            "start": "178.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The storm of gunfire was coming\nfrom Gao&#39;s central", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "187.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "courthouse, the palace\nof justice.", 
            "dur": "1.42", 
            "start": "189.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Soldiers milled around\naimlessly, preparing for", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "195.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "battle and trying to work\nout what was going on.", 
            "dur": "3.61", 
            "start": "198.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was a scene of\nutter confusion.", 
            "dur": "1.56", 
            "start": "201.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.482", 
            "start": "212.168"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-We were taking fire from\nmultiple locations.", 
            "dur": "1.675", 
            "start": "228.97"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It became clear that there were\nmore jihadists in town", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "236.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "than anyone had expected.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "239.18"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.922", 
            "start": "245.868"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-The major in charge of these\ntroops thought there were", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "247.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "snipers on top of the building\nopposite, so he sent some", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "250.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "soldiers in to check.", 
            "dur": "1.934", 
            "start": "252.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.482", 
            "start": "254.774"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "281.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-On the roof, confusion reigned\nas friendly fire threw", 
            "dur": "2.865", 
            "start": "306.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "us to the floor.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "309.215"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "334.212"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-The Malians had worked out\nthat the jihadists weren&#39;t", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "353.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just in the courthouse\nbut also in the", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "355.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "marketplace on our right.", 
            "dur": "1.61", 
            "start": "357.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They sprayed wild bursts of\nmachine gun fire at them.", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "359.18"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The soldiers exchanged\ncigarettes while the corporal", 
            "dur": "2.09", 
            "start": "367.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "worked out what to do.", 
            "dur": "3.41", 
            "start": "369.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then he rang the commanding\nofficer down below.", 
            "dur": "3.81", 
            "start": "372.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "376.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-The corporal wanted to smash\nthe wall down with an armored", 
            "dur": "2.34", 
            "start": "381.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "car and attack the Islamists,\nbut his commanding officer", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "383.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wasn&#39;t so sure.", 
            "dur": "2.447", 
            "start": "386.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.497", 
            "start": "389.047"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-The two men stood in the street\narguing about how to", 
            "dur": "2.105", 
            "start": "401.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fight the battle.", 
            "dur": "1.135", 
            "start": "403.525"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Neither of them knew the enemy\nwere about to make the", 
            "dur": "1.79", 
            "start": "404.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "decision for them.", 
            "dur": "2.048", 
            "start": "406.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[GUN FIRE]", 
            "dur": "1.976", 
            "start": "408.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.482", 
            "start": "410.474"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-The Jeep came to take the\nwounded major away.", 
            "dur": "4.275", 
            "start": "428.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[LAUGHING]", 
            "dur": "1.94", 
            "start": "433.045"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "2.435", 
            "start": "434.985"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-Now the corporal\nwas in charge.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "437.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They took the fight\nto the Islamists.", 
            "dur": "1.65", 
            "start": "438.97"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "2.904", 
            "start": "446.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-We pulled back a bit while the\narmored car drove up to", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "449.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "smash down the wall.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "452.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "2.874", 
            "start": "456.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-No one wants to drive\nthrough a minefield.", 
            "dur": "2.34", 
            "start": "459.18"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The armored car driver reversed\ndown the road to", 
            "dur": "2.697", 
            "start": "461.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "consider a more careful\napproach.", 
            "dur": "2.385", 
            "start": "464.217"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "While the vehicles considered\nthe next step, the Malian", 
            "dur": "2.83", 
            "start": "472.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "soldiers laid down a wall\nof covering fire.", 
            "dur": "2.43", 
            "start": "475.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.482", 
            "start": "490.938"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-It was a few hours into\nthe battle now.", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "498.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the soldiers were beginning\nto run out of ammo.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "501.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.479", 
            "start": "503.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-The Malians were about to\nlaunch a head-on assault on", 
            "dur": "2.35", 
            "start": "534.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the courthouse.", 
            "dur": "1.56", 
            "start": "536.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "538.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-While the jihadists were\noutnumbered and outgunned,", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "550.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they weren&#39;t giving up.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "552.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The advance faulted under the\nenemy&#39;s sustained and accurate", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "558.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "riffle fire.", 
            "dur": "1.65", 
            "start": "560.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They needed a better plan.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "562.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "17.868", 
            "start": "569.55"
        }
    ], 
